==Devanagari script==
=== Hindi ===
'''श'''

==== Pronunciation ====
/ ʃ /, pronounced alone it is / ʃə /, similar to the English ship

====Consonant====

The first [[sibilant]] of the [[Devanagari]] script. Linguistically it is considered a [[w:Voiceless postalveolar fricative|voiceless postalveolar sibilant]].

=== Transliteration ===
*[[w:IAST|IAST]]: ś or Ś
*[[w:ITRANS|ITRANS]]: sh

